handist.collections

Class ChunkedList.LongRangeOrdering

  • java.lang.Object
    • handist.collections.ChunkedList.LongRangeOrdering
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparator<LongRange>
    Enclosing class:
    ChunkedList<T>

    public static final class ChunkedList.LongRangeOrdering
extends Object
implements Comparator<LongRange>, Serializable
    Class which defines the order in which Chunks are stored in the underlying ConcurrentSkipListMap. Contrary to the default ordering of class LongRange, entries in this member will be sorted by increasing LongRange.from and decreasing LongRange.to. This simplifies a number of retrieval operations proposed by class ChunkedList as retrieving a target range
    Author:
    Patrick Finnerty
